What is the purpose of the Windows System Restore tool? It helps when you PC might be acting up and you can restore it to a early state where it was working.
How long does it usually take to use the System Restore tool in Windows? 10-30 min
How do you start a System Restore from the command prompt? Typing rstrui.exe will start the system restore 
What options are available if System Restore did not fix the problem? trouble shoot other methods if not try to restore from earlier state
